8. Questions

Why are there so many missing data for variables like temperature, elevation, and wind speed?

Is there an association between temperature and wind speed?

plot(elev$temp, elev$dew.point)

It seems that temperature and dew point at the highest elevation have a very strong positive linear relationship, which is to be expected.
